ly as her GB team-mates won 11 medals.\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1814, \"end\": 1823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archibald_Prize\", \"score\": 0.9433466583621387, \"rank\": 0.06005569627666213, \"text\": \"Archibald\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archibald_Prize\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archibald_Prize\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Surgery\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1761}, {\"ngram\": \"her fall\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"rehabilitation\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1807}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"her GB team-mates\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"11 medals\", \"from\": 1942, \"to\": 1951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't anxious to get back.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just had a serious craving to get back to training, regardless of what result it would lead to, regardless of whether I'd be any good at it It is little wonder, then, that Archibald, who spoke about losing a slight sense of identity during her time on the sidelines, is revelling being back in the saddle, irrespective of how she performs.\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2159, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archibald_Prize\", \"score\": 0.9433466583621387, \"rank\": 0.06005569627666213, \"text\": \"Archibald\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archibald_Prize\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archibald_Prize\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a serious craving\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2036}, {\"ngram\": \"little wonder\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"a slight sense\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2206}, {\"ngram\": \"identity\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2218}, {\"ngram\": \"her time\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"the sidelines\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2251}, {\"ngram\": \"the saddle\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't anxious to get back,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just had a serious craving to get back to training, regardless of what result it would lead to, regardless of whether I'd be any good at it.\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a serious craving\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2399}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's one thing to lose the Olympics but there really wasn't much you can do (wearing) a boot.\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2530}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"a boot\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got really into swimming and I did upper body work at the gym but none of it felt like a cathartic release.\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2636}, {\"ngram\": \"upper body work\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2673}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2682}, {\"ngram\": \"a cathartic release\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd lost being able to move properly.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2759, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd lost my sense of community a little bit because cycling is that community to me and and my team were off on training camps, on holding camps and at the Games.\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my sense\", \"from\": 276